Package task

Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • task.Task
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Add, DeadLine, Event, ToDo
    public class Task
extends java.lang.Object
    The `Task` class represents a generic task in the BloopBot application. It serves as the base class for different types of tasks, including Add, ToDo, DeadLine, and Event tasks. A task contains a description and can be marked as completed or not completed. It also provides methods for parsing and formatting date and time information.
    Version:
    0.0.0
    Author:
    raydenlim
